---
import ArticleLayout from '../../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';

const locale = 'en';
---

<!-- [Customize this page for your site] -->
<ArticleLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy template for a static tool site with client-side tools, optional analytics, and optional ads."
  locale={locale}
  updated="2026-06-28"
>
  <p>
    This privacy policy is a starter template. [Replace with your details],
    including your legal name, business name, address if required, and contact
    email.
  </p>
  <h2>Tool data</h2>
  <p>
    The tools on this site are intended to run client-side in your browser. We
    do not operate a custom backend that receives the text you enter into these
    tools. If a tool uses localStorage, that data stays on your device unless
    you clear it, clear your browser data, or use the tool's clear action.
  </p>
  <h2>Analytics and advertising</h2>
  <p>
    When configured, this site may use Google Analytics 4 to understand general
    traffic patterns and Google AdSense to display ads. Google services may set
    cookies or use similar technologies. You can control cookies in your browser
    settings and review Google ad personalization controls at
    https://adssettings.google.com/.
  </p>
  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Privacy contact: [Replace with your details], for example
    hello@example.com.
  </p>
</ArticleLayout>
